        "sendTo": "={{ $('Parse Email Address').first().json.to_email }}",
        "subject": "=Full Stack Developer role at {{ $('Set Job Details').first().json.company_name }}",
        "emailType": "text",
        "message": "=Hi {{ $('Parse Email Address').first().json.contact_name }},\n\nI came across the {{ $('Set Job Details').first().json.job_title }} role at {{ $('Set Job Details').first().json.company_name }} and I believe my background as a Full Stack Developer makes me a strong fit.\n\nI'd love to learn more about this opportunity and discuss how I can contribute. I've attached my resume for your reference.\n\nLinkedIn: {{ $('Set Global Vars').first().json.linkedinLink }}\nGitHub: {{ $('Set Global Vars').first().json.githubLink }}\nPortfolio: {{ $('Set Global Vars').first().json.portfolioLink }}\n\nLooking forward to connecting!\n\nBest regards,\nRahat Sayyed",
